				\begin{document}$$ \log \kern0.5em Y={\beta}_{\cap }+{{\displaystyle {\sum}_i^k\beta}}_i{\displaystyle {X}_i} $$\end{document}logY=β∩+∑ikβiXi for k independent variables and thus \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
